headline: Phillips 66: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: HOUSTON (AP) — Phillips 66 (PSX) on Wednesday reported third-quarter profit of $133 million. The Houston-based company said it had net income of 32 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, came to $2.52 per share.
